text: Andrea Waldis (born 13 June 1994) is a Swiss racing cyclist. She rode in the women's omnium event at the 2018 UCI Track Cycling World Championships. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss female cyclists Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Cyclists at the 2019 European Games Category:European Games competitors for Switzerland
